title: Where will Suh land?
itunes:title: Where will Suh land?
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- debate where Ndamukong Suh will land in free agency and discuss the franchise tags of Dez Bryant, Demaryius Thomas and more. Plus, Conor Orr calls in to discuss which teams are going to be big spenders this offseason.
